    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2096510/extras/b3f032713704d10ef85e31e091bf75fe.poster.avif?t=1771691368\" width=616 height=353 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2096510/extras/b3f032713704d10ef85e31e091bf75fe.webm?t=1771691368\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br><br>《衔尾蛇国王》结合了国际象棋的战术深度与肉鸽游戏的构筑多样性和重复游玩性，带来全新的国际象棋体验。在国际象棋规则的基础上，以棋盘为战场，指挥各式各样的棋子进行战斗、发现能提供永久增益的远古遗物、购买效果强劲的魔法道具，最终战胜邪恶女巫集会，夺回塞萨洛尼亚王国吧！<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2096510/extras/93de72321c0f55f0c1d42144bd1270bf.webp?t=1771691368\" width=616 height=59 /></span><br><br>游戏内有超过50种不同的可用棋子，包含经典的国象棋子与精心设计的新式棋子，许多棋子能通过升级变得更加强大！招募各具特色的棋子，壮大你的部队。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2096510/extras/6c3f0d5509037ea755a5d18c7e6bf821.avif?t=1771691368\" width=616 height=355 /></span><br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2096510/extras/805c2e6e71f7b97f15fe692352831d6f.webp?t=1771691368\" width=616 height=59 /></span><br><br>在夺回王国的征途中，留心那些埋藏在遗迹中的远古遗物，它们能提供永久性的增益效果，在战斗中为你提供帮助。但要注意，敌人也会利用遗物的力量协助战斗！<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2096510/extras/e959983986e306d6bae4ab693b0566ef.avif?t=1771691368\" width=616 height=355 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2096510/extras/629dd4f0dcf5a3f490aa50750bf722d8.webp?t=1771691368\" width=616 height=59 /></span><br><br>在商店花费金币购买魔法道具，一次性的消耗换来的是无比强大的效果：改变棋子行动模式、封锁敌方行动、放置极具杀伤的炸弹……在合适的时机使用魔法道具，颠覆整个战局吧。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2096510/extras/fdbc6f0c37a2582fe87a529fa5500794.avif?t=1771691368\" width=616 height=355 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2096510/extras/8d4bd681b5cdfa11e3b2d32e65e8cc84.webp?t=1771691368\" width=616 height=59 /></span><br><br>在战胜或是战败后，你都可以到达另一条时间线，胜利之道也会随之发生改变：不同的地图、不同的敌人、不同的奖励……<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2096510/extras/c5ed72d0361cd3b209e4672900341e13.avif?t=1771691368\" width=616 height=355 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >更多特色：</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>大量的残局选项可供选择，提升难度挑战自我<br></li><li>以国际象棋为基础，易上手难精通<br></li><li>一轮游戏大概15-45分钟，适合短暂的放松，也能作为长时间的棋技训练<br></li><li>无门槛，所有内容都已解锁，输赢只取决于你的技巧<br></li><li>无需提前学习国际象棋开局或研究任何战术<br><br>游戏插图由Isaac Murgadella绘制</li></ul>",
